{"tid":98232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]年初一 十五 條禁忌你犯左邊條","createTime":"2017-01-28T09:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T11:04:08.000Z","uid":73953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ffb9e3e3a5deee13c096bb941766731f983fd2","tid":98232,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:00:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1.已出嫁的女兒不可以回娘家</span><br />\n<br />\n意指著會把娘家吃窮<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.早餐忌吃稀飯、葷食及藥品</span><br />\n<br />\n過去的傳統窮人家才吃稀飯，<br />\n所以在年初一的上午一定要吃乾飯，<br />\n表示家裡整年度都會很富有，<br />\n而年初一的早上叫做萬神盛會，<br />\n表示所有的神出來拜年，<br />\n因此為表尊敬首先不要吃葷，要吃素，<br />\n另外除了重病不得不吃之外，<br />\n一般的補品補藥初一最好不要吃。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.忌叫他人姓名催人起床</span><br />\n<br />\n年初一的上午不要叫人姓名催人起床，<br />\n這樣表示對方整年度都要人催促做事情。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.忌跟還在睡覺的人拜年</span><br />\n<br />\n年初一時對方還在睡夢中不要跟對方拜年，<br />\n等對方起床再拜年，<br />\n因為這樣會讓對方一整年都在病床中。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5.忌吃藥</span><br />\n<br />\n說是&ldquo;初一吃藥一整年，<br />\n而且咩病也治不好&rdquo;，<br />\n所以除了重病不得不吃以外，<br />\n初一最好不要吃藥。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6.禁忌動刀子和剪子</span>(岩岩電視節目有小朋友做剪貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n說是&ldquo;初一動了刀和剪，<br />\n口舌是非全難免&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7.忌動針線</span><br />\n<br />\n說是&ldquo;初一動了針線，<br />\n挑了龍筋長針眼&rdquo;。<br />\n(生下的小孩，眼睛如同針眼一樣小)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8.忌斧子劈木柴</span><br />\n<br />\n說是&ldquo;初一斧子劈開柴(財)，<br />\n劈開再也回不來&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n[url]9.忌借錢[/url]<br />\n<br />\n說是&ldquo;初一借了別人的錢，<br />\n一年四季靠外援；<br />\n初一借給別人錢，財產外流一整年&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10.忌打碎家具</span><br />\n<br />\n打碎家具，一年四季都會不吉利。不過在當今社會，<br />\n當孩子們由於不慎打碎了家具也不要緊，<br />\n只要大人們趕快說上一句：<br />\n&ldquo;歲(碎)來(了)好，歲來好，歲歲平安&rdquo;，也就化兇為吉了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">11.白天不可午睡</span><br />\n<br />\n過年期間白天睡午覺，<br />\n表示整年度都會很懶惰，<br />\n其中的含意是因為過年期間有很多客人到家裡拜年，<br />\n如果睡午覺的話對人很失禮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">12.忌倒污水、垃圾、掃地</span><br />\n<br />\n過年期間不要從事灑掃的工作，<br />\n因為這樣容易把家中的財氣掃掉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">13.忌被他人自口袋掏取物件</span><br />\n<br />\n過年期間不要讓人從自己口袋掏東西，<br />\n這樣表示整年度錢財都會被人家掏走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">14.忌向人討債</span><br />\n<br />\n過年期間不管是被要債或者<br />\n是跟人家要債的人在一整年間都會很倒楣，<br />\n因此忌諱向人討債。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">15.忌洗衣</span><br />\n<br />\n因為水神生日....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cmoney.tw/notes/note-detail.aspx?nid=24707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmoney.tw%2Fnotes%2Fnote-detail.aspx%3Fnid%3D24707&d=a6jwj76mG8mcAc9%2FaZOaenvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c2601e9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cmoney.tw/notes/note-detail.aspx?nid=24707</a>"},{"pid":"e8b7a84e55b4a1a4c3ab7f1ffa4f25b82840515f","tid":98232,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"201a5b3b432a885a7bc899f347bfb317c4a6db4c","tid":98232,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on99</blockquote><br />\n呢d係美麗既中華民族傳統文化之一<br />\n唔可以話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02db1d5af9b2a004b54309907d44e1094815dc77","tid":98232,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fbe39a61c65cda481c8485863aa352903473059c","tid":98232,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:11:06.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a57f60065030f21c4e29454c9ec1714213d0168e","tid":98232,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"3<br />\n<br />\n十連不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f568aca60b8656e935a0cbda77ce4b784b1e8876","tid":98232,"uid":36553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:21:57.000Z","msg":"斷"},{"pid":"de416d2f92f8434755be2d43ad1df86ceb722021","tid":98232,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:25:12.000Z","msg":"應該係問有邊條冇犯"},{"pid":"336909dda77e29f31786ba6dab8856d41a3ec925","tid":98232,"uid":31777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"如果換個角度<br />\n做以上嘅事係有好處<br />\n但被既得利益者抹黑為禁忌<br />\n有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb85b71886fe3b110c5094bd75a1dfb4da175c7b","tid":98232,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果換個角度<br />\n做以上嘅事係有好處<br />\n但被既得利益者抹黑為禁忌<br />\n有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明"},{"pid":"c3b74976922c1b41396c3072653a13c348e4d9e0","tid":98232,"uid":73953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係問有邊條冇犯</blockquote><br />\n除左11 其餘都冇犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a52d3cdd14dcd3634bb11041b65680b888a64a5","tid":98232,"uid":31777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果換個角度<br />\n做以上嘅事係有好處<br />\n但被既得利益者抹黑為禁忌<br />\n有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比如新年問人借錢會發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藉新年借錢發咗達嘅人就話<br />\n「問人借錢會窮 唔好借」<br />\n拎完好處再去作故仔隱瞞或抹黑<br />\n<br />\n利申：小學生"}]}